<br>
For my part its obvious.  Im stuck at my Jade Reaver.  Its not likely that I can get a single group together and get this item by myself.  This isnt the Dark Elf Corruptor in ek.  My answer is to organize a CoM riad and post it.  Now as Vig has pointed out this is a selfish practice on my part and I want to start correcting this and give back to the Federation.  But I cant do this if i dont know where we need to go and who we need to kill.<br>
<br>
So tell me.  Where do we need to raid.  What massive fights do we need to fight.  Just remember im not talking about raids for armor and other items.  Im talking Epic Level fights that require multiple groups.<br>
<br>
Thank You<br>
